prompt: "Create the file `mcp_terminal/jobs/terminal_execution_job.py`.\n\nOperation:\
  \ create_file\n\nAlso create `mcp_terminal/jobs/__init__.py` as an empty file with\
  \ only a\nmodule docstring:\n  \"\"\"\n  Queue job implementations for mcp_terminal.\n\
