  \ ContainerSpec\n  timeout_seconds: int\n\n### class TerminalExecutionJob\nDocstring:\n\
  \  \"\"\"Queue job that performs sandbox container execution (C-009).\n\n  The run()\
  \ method is called by the adapter queue worker in a background\n  thread. It must\
  \ never be called directly from request handlers.\n  QueueResultSemantics (C-011):\
